Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.34,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据悉  同盟军傍晚便能抵达这片战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总兵力约有4万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4万…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家明白  这反倒少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟经历了先前的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.28,0:00:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德和诺尔德已经损耗不少兵力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联合真的会来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.66,0:00:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息称正在赶来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.12,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过  貌似要到明天正午时分才能抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好迟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这场战斗中  我方无需主动出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只需守到在联合抵达即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束这场大战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.16,0:01:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一切将尘埃落定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知打头阵的纳约达公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及第二阵的夏安公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上  我们的神兽伽伽诺特所向无敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳约达公将为我们开辟道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切莫贪功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魔兽突破阵地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵大军再压上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像父亲的风格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好现实的战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我方就用奇计应对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该撤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨呀  把箭楼拆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.81,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放过这机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入苦战了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派库班公和卡里姆伯爵支援前线吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺尔德那边还没好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说即将进攻哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们抓紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺尔德的长船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被哈鲁西亚公打得那么残了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还能派出军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.29,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这恐怕是诺尔德目前能动用的最大兵力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击退他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区哈曼的船  看我不沉了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我父亲埃里克见识一场光荣的战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是火船哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那么容易烧上我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把道让开  让船飘到海里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢在战场上分心愚蠢之极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从侧面渐渐削减兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人数量太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去就要被夹击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏安公和纳约达公的军队已经重整完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.60,0:07:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库班公和卡里姆伯爵也正按原计划从两翼进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离突破敌阵只差一点助力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要出击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德军出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.82,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩特尔  通知拉席克  一边战斗一边撤回大本营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后在这里防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要亲自上阵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会单挑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄提欧来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人顶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,架起重弩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装填圣印弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别退缩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.80,0:09:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来带你们上路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴尔加利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别落后哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵第二阵  与重装骑兵一同进军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反弹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须撑到联合抵达…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟的大部队出动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方用全军对抗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是联合的军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们撑住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.56,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退重整旗鼓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去退路会被断掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.45,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强撑住了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也撤退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.38,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 申请三盟主会谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.26,0:12:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我提两个建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.16,0:12:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是  同盟联合条约这三势力缔结友好条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无稽之谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.75,0:12:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结友好条约？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会便宜了盘踞在这片土地的真正的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的敌人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引发大圣堂惨剧的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  应该是从更早的时代就暗中控制这片大地的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下应该知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  三势力缔结友好条约的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将维持爵位制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即维持魔法师协会定下的维持现状的规矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.49,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师协会给予我等君主爵位这一诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无异于被控制的家畜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要缔结友好条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因我们这些君主相互对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕爵位不断争斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协会的管理才会持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.68,0:13:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现状才是正中了协会的下怀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那帮人想必不愿看见我们缔结友好条约吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会用阴谋让我们破裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听一下我的第二个建议吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三势力缔结友好条约的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.83,0:14:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯•德赛与玛丽娜•克莱榭成婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位就让圣印统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我  将从属那个圣印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.09,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想在此时让皇帝圣印诞生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样只会重复惨剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印一旦统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必协会终将与我们为敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我才想着一个人战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.19,0:14:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让敌人的矛头只对准我一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.62,0:14:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也能让全大陆的人知道真正的敌人是谁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了又能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一日会有人继承我的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的任务到此便足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用终有一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿莱克希斯大人现在就要跟你并肩作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我万万不能答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.39,0:15:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么如此执着于独自承担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人牺牲简直太荒唐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们三人一起面对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对真正的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把阿莱克希斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵扯进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论敌人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想跟你一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能跟我走一趟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.84,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能当我的妃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.01,0:16:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的圣印也好  生命也好  爱也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部献给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没资格接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经对达尔塔尼亚太子以身相许了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毫无疑问  我已失去清白身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱过达尔塔尼亚太子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.09,0:17:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就毫无问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.64,0:17:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是我爱着你  你是否会接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我浑身已被血玷污
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.07,0:17:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我  成干上万的人失去了生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没资格获得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你没资格获得幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我也一起承担这惩罚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们穷尽一生去赎罪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经娶西露卡为妃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还未公布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打从心底爱着西露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她接受了我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相爱的两个人结合是一件自然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界不允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算得摧毁世界 我也想改变这样的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.42,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的愿意娶我为妃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说多少次都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上有多少星星  我就可以重复多少遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经理解了爱是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我在遇见你之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.23,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了爱上一个人是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请成为我的妃子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单单是注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能感受到至高无上的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无可饶恕的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.00,0:19:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为阿莱克希斯・德赛的妃子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该从属于哪一方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们从属于你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是心怀疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗究竟是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  我感觉终于想明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的祖父约根曾认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.22,0:20:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统一大陆必须将世界推倒重建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下  你正准备这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是改成为始皇的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就答应了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在奇迹实现之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再将圣印还给阿莱克希斯大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜大人既是媳子也是宰相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而提欧大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我们回到西斯迪纳就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这才是提欧大人最后的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知大陆这件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似不太平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.72,0:22:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正动用特务机关  肃清君主派的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.56,0:22:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？三势力会战时发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.27,0:23:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝圣印即将诞生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.98,0:23:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.90,0:23:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与君主们的对决已不可避免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.90,0:23:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我等魔法师协会也必须团结一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了阻止秩序时代的来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.50,0:23:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现那人的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的意志啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我行动的时候也快到了啊
